---
title: Chicken and Mixed Mushroom Risotto with Fried Sage Leaves
description: This dish takes flavour inspiration from your favourite trattoria! Hearty broth plumps up each grain of rice to create an irresistibly creamy risotto, finished with hearty chicken. A sprinkle of fragrant, crispy sage leaves will make you feel like a top chef!
